node.text:
We are announcing Community Challenges. Here comes the first one: «Standard Bearer».
— Drop to any map in the Capture mode.
— Carry the enemy flag for 30 seconds outside the bases on a map.
— Win the match
Additional mission:
— Kill 3+ enemies
⠀
Rewards:
Top 10 participant will get 300 gems, plus 1000 coins if additional mission is complete.
⠀
How to participate:
1. Record your successful game
2. Upload the video to YouTube. It MUST have the following name «Pixel Gun 3D Standard Bearer Challenge»
3. Max one entry per player.
4. We will stop submissions on Monday, August 12.
***
In this video you can see how one of the devs, desperaterussian, completes this challenge.
Aaaand, yeah, remember, those, who complete the mission faster than others will definitely receive the prize.
Good luck!
⠀
#PixelGun3D #pg3d #pixelgun

node.text:
We've got a HUGE announcement for you today. We've made our first Dev Update! 🤩
⠀
What's that? 🤔
Well, this is the format in which we'll tell you a little bit about our plans for the future and show you some upcoming new features.
⠀
Follow the LINK in STORIES to see the Pixel Gun 3D Dev Update#1
⠀
Which of these changes are you most looking forward to?
⠀
#PixelGun3D #pg3d #pixelgun

We found four more suspects in this tangled case. You can see their faces in the picture 🦹‍♂️

node.text:
⚠️WARNING⚠️ These dangerous criminals hacked into our secret servers and stole valuable data - a piece of code, without which the game can not exist 🤯

We're announcing a reward for 10 players who will decipher the full piece of code – 💎 1000 GEMS!

Your task is to:
1️⃣ Find the stolen letters in the last videos of these criminals;
2️⃣ Make a phrase out of them;
3️⃣ Send it to us via Google Forms.

We've figured out 4 of them, but rumor has it there's more of them... So we are continuing our investigation and will be sure to let you know as soon as we find the rest of the bad guys😈

🚨We'll also post the form as soon as we find the remaining members of this gang🚨

Good luck, detectives. Together we will save Pixel Gun 3D! 💪

#pg3d #pixelgun #pixelgun3d
